name: Snakebite
explicitMods: 2% increased Attack Speed per Frenzy Charge
6% increased Accuracy Rating per Frenzy Charge
10% reduced Frenzy Charge Duration per Frenzy Charge
When at maximum Frenzy Charges, Attacks Poison enemies
flavourText: "As the serpent shuns thought,
It shuns fear.
It strikes with the speed of wrath
And the skill of compulsion."
- Deshret, The Red Sekhema

name: The Coward's Trial
explicitMods: Area has 33 seconds between monster waves
descrText: Travel to this Map by using it in the Eternal Laboratory. Maps can only be used once.
flavourText: For his sins he was hunted in his sleep,
judgement wrought of twisted nightmare.
The Coward bound his dreams to stone, awaiting
another to walk the path of true atonement.

name: Soul Mantle
explicitMods: Gems in this item are Supported by level 14 Spell Totem
Can summon up to 1 additional totem
Inflicts a random level 20 Curse on you when your Totems die
flavourText: The greatest mistakes cause suffering
long after they have been made

name: Reaper's Pursuit
explicitMods: 15% increased Movement Speed when on Full Life
flavourText: Accept your fate, or lie, pretend.
Death collects you in the end.

In order to receive, one must give... without hesitation.

name: Hrimnor's Hymn
explicitMods: 5% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Life
flavourText: "The crack of bone, the spray of blood.
Is there sweeter music?"
- Hrimnor of the Ezomytes.

name: Geofri's Baptism
flavourText: "One quick tap is all the persuasion you'll need."
- Archbishop Geofri of Phrecia Cathedral

name: Death's Harp
flavourText: The mournful music of the strings,
The creaking arch, the arrow sings.
A choking cry, a rattled breath,
The Reaper's Song, the Harp of Death.

name: Daresso's Courage
explicitMods: 120% of Block Chance applied to Spells when on Low Life
flavourText: By tourney's end, Daresso bled and shivered.
Yet even accursed treachery failed to steal the champion's victory.

name: Blackgleam
explicitMods: 41% of Physical Damage Converted to Fire Damage
flavourText: Molten feathers, veiled spark,
Hissing arrows from the dark.

name: Fairgraves' Tricorne
flavourText: Fairgraves' trusty tricorne accompanied him far across
the seas, deep under the ground, and even beyond death.

name: Mindspiral
explicitMods: Enemies Cannot Leech Mana From You
6% of Damage taken Gained as Mana when Hit
flavourText: Where top is bottom and weak is strong.

name: Honourhome
explicitMods: 20% increased Elemental Resistances while on Low Life

flavourText: "The craven mind is sharp with self interest.
The honourable mind is much easier to manipulate."
- Malachai the Soulless

name: Doedre's Tenure
